                                                 Writ                                                 
                                                                                                          
                                                                                                          
                                                                                                          
         Find the differences ...                                                                         
                                                                                                          
                                                                                                          
           #[writ::task]                                   #[ink::task]                                   
           pub mod flipper {                               pub mod flipper {                              
             #[writ(storage)]                                #[ink(storage)]                              
             pub struct Flipper { value: bool }              pub struct Flipper { value: bool }           
             impl Flipper {                                  impl Flipper {                               
               //...                                           //...                                      
               #[writ(message)]                                #[ink(message)]                            
               pub async fn flip(&mut self) {                  pub fn flip(&mut self) {                   
                 self.value = !self.value;                       self.value = !self.value;                
               }                                               }                                          
             }                                               }                                            
           }                                               }                                       9 / 12
